msgid "Smoker"
msgstr "훈연기"

msgid "Cooks food faster than furnace"
msgstr "화로보다 빠르게 조리"

msgid "Smokers cook several items, mainly raw foods, into cooked foods, but twice as fast as a normal furnace."
msgstr ""
"훈연기는 주로 날것을 포함한 여러 아이템을 익혀 음식을 만들며, 일반 화로보다 "
"두 배 빠르게 조리합니다."

msgid "Use the smoker to open the furnace menu."
msgstr "훈연기를 사용하여 요리 창을 열 수 있습니다."

msgid "Place a furnace fuel in the lower slot and the source material in the upper slot."
msgstr ""

msgid "The smoker will slowly use its fuel to smelt the item."
msgstr ""

msgid "The result will be placed into the output slot at the right side."
msgstr ""

msgid "Use the recipe book to see what foods you can smelt, what you can use as fuel and how long it will burn."
msgstr ""

msgid "Burning Smoker"
msgstr ""
